  Locus:
    Page: 212
    Verse: 1
Tags:
  - Grief
---
The root cause of man’s grief and delusion is the identification of the
Soul with the body. Fear of death paralyzes him because he is ignorant of
the Soul’s true nature. The wise perform their duties in the world,
cherishing always the knowledge of the Soul’s deathlessness.
